Guidelines for submitting your homework programs
	
- Please write down your personal information as well as 
   course information in the program you submit. 
   For example, see HW Program Example
- Please use the HW number and your student ID as the filename 
   that is,  HW1B92901XXX.m 
- Please e-mail your HW programs to differnt desinaged HW TA
		   by 9AM of the due date

		- Late HW submissions will only get partial grade.  
   That is, 0~1 day: 90% of your grade; 1~2 days: 80%; etc.

	



	



          


Please visit the Main Course Website for the detailed information
	about the homework sets.
	


